  {
    "ghsa_id": "GHSA-rmp6-jjg8-9424",
    "cve_id": "CVE-2020-11057",
    "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/xwiki/xwiki-platform/security-advisories/GHSA-rmp6-jjg8-9424",
    "html_url": "https://github.com/xwiki/xwiki-platform/security/advisories/GHSA-rmp6-jjg8-9424",
    "summary": "Authenticated server side code execution without programming rights on User Dashboards",
    "description": "### Impact\r\nRegistered users without scripting/programming permissions are able to execute python/groovy scripts while editing personal dashboards.\r\nThe problem was already there in XWiki 7.2 until XWiki 11.10.3.\r\n\r\n### Patches\r\nIt has been patched and released in both version XWiki 11.10.3 and XWiki 12.0. You can [upgrade XWiki](https://www.xwiki.org/xwiki/bin/view/Documentation/AdminGuide/Upgrade) to those versions and it will automatically contain the patch.\r\n\r\nYou can also try to manually retrieve the patched jar on Maven and replace your current one with it:\r\n  - [version 11.10.3 available on Nexus XWiki](http://nexus.xwiki.org/nexus/content/groups/public/org/xwiki/platform/xwiki-platform-dashboard-macro/11.10.3/xwiki-platform-dashboard-macro-11.10.3.jar)\r\n  - [version 12.0 available on Nexus XWiki](http://nexus.xwiki.org/nexus/content/groups/public/org/xwiki/platform/xwiki-platform-dashboard-macro/12.0/xwiki-platform-dashboard-macro-12.0.jar)\r\n\r\nFinally, you can also cherry-pick the fix committed on https://github.com/xwiki/xwiki-platform/commit/dc0fa65fa1c55360dd428106ded5934e7caa59b1#diff-1d01d375880acfb72b454faca73d23a8 for a specific version and build xwiki-platform-dashboard-macro manually.\r\n\r\n### Workarounds\r\nIt is strongly recommended to upgrade XWiki version.\r\nThe only workaround for this issue is to completely remove the Dashboard Macro feature from XWiki, by removing `xwiki-platform-dashboard-macro.jar` in `datadir/webapps/xwiki/WEB-INF/lib`.\r\nYou can then check that it has been correctly removed by going in the Administration > Extensions, and by looking for \"Dashboard Macro\" in \"Core extensions\".\r\n\r\n### References\r\nhttps://jira.xwiki.org/browse/XWIKI-16960\r\n\r\n### For more information\r\nIf you have any questions or comments about this advisory:\r\n* Open an issue in [Jira XWiki](https://jira.xwiki.org)\r\n* Email us at [our security mailing list](mailto:security@xwiki.org)\r\n",
